    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>Hello dear reader! </p>
<p><img src="http://1-ps.googleusercontent.com/x/s.google-melange.appspot.com/www.google-melange.com/soc/content/2-1-20131128/images/gci/xblock-how-it-works-more.jpg.pagespeed.ic.XJL9NLhzZy.jpg" /></p>
<p>At this post I would like to talk, how to help Drupal and get prizes from Google. This post is intended for pre-university students, who like to programming, interface design, or writing documentation for software products and like Drupal of course. if you are such a student, I suggest you take part in the <a href="?q=node/4">Google Code-In</a>.</p>
<!--break--><p>
At first you have to <a href="?q=node/5">Sign up</a> on Code-in.<br />
Then you can <a href="http://www.google-melange.com/gci/org/google/gci2013/drupal">find a task by Drupal</a>.<br />
Select a task from the task list. Please choose a task suited to your skills.<br />
I advise you, as well you must learn the basics of GIT. Git is really helpful program, it have very many features that can help you in your Code-In tasks.<br />
With it you can: copy the code repository and synchronize it with the latest updates, check the changes in some file and make commit, send your commit to Drupal.org or extract it like a patch.</p>
<p></p><h5>What about tasks?</h5>
<p>I chose such task:<br /><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/vpdu9rp08t0tukj/Скриншот%202013-12-05%2015.32.35.png" /></p>
<p>Same there are tasks:<br /><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/277c7pok6wxsrtb/Скриншот%202013-12-05%2016.08.16.png" /></p>
<p>and</p>
<p><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/j1gz6gb2vn18cm7/%D0%A1%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%88%D0%BE%D1%82%202013-12-05%2017.19.12.png" /></p>
<p></p><h5>Task claiming and working</h5>
<ul><li>
Just click "Claim this task!" button<br /><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/8tskboyyndw2ivm/%D0%A1%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%88%D0%BE%D1%82%202013-12-05%2017.24.11.png" /></li>
<li>
<p>Wait for a message from a mentor "a task assigned"<br /><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/3ahenimqeux0hwf/%D0%A1%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%88%D0%BE%D1%82%202013-12-05%2017.30.19.png" /></p></li>
<li>you can start working!</li>
</ul><p>if you do not understand the conditions of the task, contact with mentor by IRC.<br />
if you can not perform the task, do not worry, just click "unclaim task" and try another task.</p>
<p>That's all. If you have any questions, ask them in the comments. Good luck!</p>
